The part I think you’re reaching toward is this:

Life computes.

Not in the sense that cells are literally running Python.

But in the sense that they continuously transform information according to rules while interacting with an environment.

Development computes.

Evolution computes.

Immune systems compute.

Brains compute.

Ecosystems compute.

